        <item>
            <title>為運動愛好者特別設計   Amazfit Up 開放式無線耳機發表</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/22/amazfit-up-open-ear-earbuds-launched/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=amazfit-up-open-ear-earbuds-launched</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/22/amazfit-up-open-ear-earbuds-launched/mobile-music/headphones/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[唐美鳳]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 05:00:05 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[音樂耳機]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Amazfit Up]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1270661</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>智能穿戴裝置品牌 Amazfit 近日發表了新款開放式耳機 Amazfit Up，專為運動健身愛好者和追求便利的用家設計。與傳統的無線耳機不同，Amazfit Up 採用夾耳式造型和開放式設計，讓用戶的耳道保持開放，不但佩戴起來更加舒適，亦能夠保持對周圍環境的感知。</p><p><span id="more-1270661"></span></p><p>Amazfit Up 耳機內置 AI 演算法，能夠在通話時有效減低背景噪音，即使在嘈雜環境亦可以保持通話清晰。當與 Amazfit 智能手錶配對時，用家更可獲取實時運動數據更新和導航提示。Amazfit Up 每隻耳機重量僅 5 克，並具備 IP54 防塵防水功能。耳機支援藍牙 5.3 和多點連接，同時連接兩部裝置亦無難度。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_28294"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/28im03r9Wzg?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>售價 49.99 美元（約 389 港元）的 Amazfit Up，廠方單次充電可提供長達 6 小時續航力，加上充電盒可額外提供 18 小時的電量，而充電盒只需 2 小時即可透過 USB-C 完全充電。耳機只有黑色磨砂一個版本，機身配備實體按鈕，方便用家控制播放、接聽電話和啟動語音助手。</p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://www.gizmochina.com/2024/10/20/amazfit-up-open-ear-earbuds-launched/">gizmochina</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/06/amazfithelioring-review/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】Amazfit Helio Ring 開箱評測　睡覺佩戴無感</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/22/amazfit-up-open-ear-earbuds-launched/mobile-music/headphones/">為運動愛好者特別設計   Amazfit Up 開放式無線耳機發表</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
